LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"64d6fa7d349c93ff2bafe07a6e43d896e1443127","tid":1548740,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:03:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=7d05fa3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"0c0da9f5f5c9d888150ac8fd77f1bb7cb9cd677f","tid":1548740,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},{"pid":"650977b4ec0b7b75ba3949b5aa4f8563c49acff9","tid":1548740,"uid":163771,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:28:12.000Z","msg":"岩呀，太子站831果日發生既事。<br />\n<br />\n事實：<br />\n警察無差別攻擊 （有片<br />\n片段中見現場有多名受傷流血人士<br />\n有片段拍到警察在為一名傷者進行急救<br />\n事發時阻止記者進行實時採訪<br />\n事件發生約2.5小時後才送傷者去醫院（已証<br />\n太子站封站2日<br />\n<br />\n結合以上，<br />\n於正常推論下，<br />\n都是發生了重大事件，<br />\n可以嚴重懷疑當中有人命傷亡<br />\n而警方並沒有滿足公眾的知情權<br />\n<br />\n在這事上需要滿足公眾知情權的是香港警方。<br />\n<br />\n責任不在受傷者，不在受害者，更不在他們的家屬。<br />\n<br />\n就算家屬出來，警方不承認的話，都唔會fact check到。依然會被懷疑是否作故仔。<br />\n<br />\n到底大家係<span style=\"color: red;\">場地</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">證人</span>仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">證物</span>都係晒警方到既事上面，想憑外面既人fact check 到d咩？？？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只有相信並迫說謊的對方露出馬腳，再由漏洞中一步步進迫，依家要集中要求公開港鐵CCTV</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc4debad745fdc598003bb7985b45b67f8bd8c79","tid":1548740,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:28:34.000Z","msg":"即使地鐵當局交出原本無缺的全方位秘路電視，也無補於事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家連cctv片都話係假，咁繼續WhatsApp 證據當真"},{"pid":"151f2b6dd121d6db0fe1855ab68b24ac6c8d1399","tid":1548740,"uid":34334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed73ffb5efa0ec02ef908a5013b8a057679dad35","tid":1548740,"uid":57723,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"大家想要既 fat cheque 應係死者彈返起身同人講佢死左<br />\n或者缺席同學請舉手個類<br />\n乜都鳩叫fat cheque真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"82742516587d50f47f08d417ace2a18b0bbeebb4","tid":1548740,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"所以咬住CCTV 先，其他就等有CCTV 再算<br />\n因為如果本身冇發生既事，check 極都係冇<br />\n塔西佗陷阱，若公權力失去其公信力，無論如何發言或是處事，社會均將給予其負面評價。<br />\n依加黨鐵同狗講咩你都覺得佢係講大話"},{"pid":"064c2fb3a49ba13f8e796c13520bab420df549f4","tid":1548740,"uid":88167,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"其實佢意思即係，根本唔洗咩fact check，因為真正係&quot;fact&quot;既，係一睇就知，唔會話你要check左先係<br />\n例如「禁止記者及急救人員進內幾個小時」，E D野先係大家都知(絕對唔會錯，個個都望住)，亦係最重要(違反人道、公眾知情權etc)。文宣上捉住E點講，黑警/政府點反駁都死，亦可以用黎拉住民意<br />\n<br />\n但「有無人死」，E個其實真係好難查，無論咩證據出左黎，都一定有位反駁到(假片、假人證...etc)，結果當大家執著於「有無人死」一點既時候就會失左焦，忘記「禁止記者及急救人員進內幾個小時」先係件事最離譜既點<br />\n<br />\n套落新屋嶺事件，其實一樣<br />\n有無女義士被強姦、輪姦/被咩人(公安定黑狗)搞，E D好多都係好難查而點查都一定有反駁點，但「被捕者被延遲送院、被捕後權利被剝奪(拖延見律師」E D就係鐵一般事實，<strong><ins>唔洗查都可以用黎證明班黑警有幾離譜</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"1c756908793c4ef291a9c42ae76a15f717fb5697","tid":1548740,"uid":88167,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"推，其實佢講野不無道理<br />\n想反駁既話，試下唔好淨鬧話佢無食藥乜乜柒柒，理性分析返佢講既野再反，盲反既話就同無腦藍絲係一樣"},{"pid":"4d5e0c86d6c795901b5579b8e34ce4e63afdca11","tid":1548740,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"992b3c5ad6b60b79cb81c821d60a73f8acc9de27","tid":1548740,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f6f08e1c157b8ea1e9fb841f5d2c9bb9028834","tid":1548740,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"今日機場因帶豬咀被拉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1548865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9月9號，星期一，行動Post！豬嘴有理，面巾無罪！反蒙面法！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong> 和理罩 - 唔使上罐反濫捕</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FGNbvKC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFGNbvKC.gif&h=9481f838&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8d6b983bb71f9a8b7eeadc92589a57e7cfb0671","tid":1548740,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:04:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又陳雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請善用不推文回覆</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9752b7be5915cf71b200d578425184b84ad7336d","tid":1548740,"uid":21275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de22bd924217e1dfa6fa88b73ec08a702465d058","tid":1548740,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:07:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50c04e1bc2505b6aefac5e74